Sentencas: A novel composite oxide Ce(Mn,Fe)O-2-La(Sr)Fe(Mn)O-3 (CFM-LSFM) was synthesized and evaluated as both anode and cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: A novel doped CeO2-LaFeO3 composite oxide as both anode and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cell with CFM-LSFM electrodes was fabricated by tape-casting and screen printing technique.
Titulo: A novel doped CeO2-LaFeO3 composite oxide as both anode and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The powergenerating performance of this cell was comparable to that of the cell with Ni-SSZ anode and LSM-SSZ cathode.
Titulo: A novel doped CeO2-LaFeO3 composite oxide as both anode and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: During the 120 h long-term test in hydrogen at 800 degrees C, the performance increased by 8.6% from 256 to 278 mW cm(-2).
Titulo: A novel doped CeO2-LaFeO3 composite oxide as both anode and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This was attributed to the decrease of polarization resistance and ohmic resistance during the test.
Titulo: A novel doped CeO2-LaFeO3 composite oxide as both anode and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The XRD results showed the presence of Fe, MnO and some unknown second phases after heat-treating the electrode materials in H-2 which may be beneficial to the anode electrochemical process.
Titulo: A novel doped CeO2-LaFeO3 composite oxide as both anode and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The gradual decrease of polarization resistance as increasing the current density possibly resulted from the increasing content of water in the anode.
Titulo: A novel doped CeO2-LaFeO3 composite oxide as both anode and cathode for solid oxide fuel cells
